HEADWORD: Planer tree
<hw>Plan"er tree`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From <person>J. S.
<etsep>Planer</etsep></person>, a German botanist.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A small-leaved North American tree (<spn>Planera
aquatica</spn>) related to the elm, but having a wingless, nutlike
fruit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

